to emergenze - aggiornamento 27 marzo |date=2020-03-27 |website=Istituto per la Sicurezza Sociale |language=it |access-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327134149/http://www.iss.sm/on-line/home/articolo49014186.html |archive-date=27 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|Malta}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Malta|Malta]]\n|241\n|0\n|5\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|MNE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Montenegro|Montenegro]]\n|233\n|2\n|1\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|KOS}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Kosovo|Kosovo]]\n|170\n|4\n|24\n|<ref>{{Citation |title=2020 coronavirus pandemic in Kosovo |date=2020-03-25 |url=https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=2020_coronavirus_pandemic_in_Kosovo&oldid=947299455 |work=Wikipedia |language=en |access-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406000620/https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=2020_coronavirus_pandemic_in_Kosovo&oldid=947299455 |archive-date=6 April 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|LIE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Liechtenstein|Liechtenstein]]\n|77\n|1\n|0\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.volksblatt.li/default.aspx |title=Aktuelle Nachrichten aus Liechtenstein - volksblatt.li |website=Liechtensteiner Volksblatt |language=de-DE |access-date=11 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217222906/https://www.volksblatt.li/default.aspx |archive-date=17 February 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|MON}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Monaco|Monaco]]\n|73\n|1\n|3\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|VAT}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Vatican City|Vatican City]]\n|7\n|0\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.vaticannews.va/en/vatican-city/news/2020-03/coronavirus-pope-positive-vatican-santa-marta-holy-see.html |title=Covid-19: 2 new cases in the Vatican, another 170 people tested - Vatican News |date=2020-03-26 |publisher=Vaticannews.va |access-date=2020-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328205016/https://www.vaticanne