]]''\n|Foggle / Guardian Angel\n|\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Better Watch Out (film)|Better Watch Out]]''\n|Robert\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Austin Found]]''\n|Chief Williams\n|\n|-\n|2019\n|''[[The Wedding Year]]''\n|Michael\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Inheritance (2020 film)|Inheritance]]''\n| Archer Monroe\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n====Television====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1986\n| ''[[The Paper Chase (TV series)|The Paper Chase]]''\n| Pool Boy\n| Episode: \"Honor\"\n|-\n| 1990\n| ''[[Quantum Leap]]''\n| Blaster\n| Episode: \"The Leap Home: Part 2 (Vietnam) \u2013 April 7, 1970\"\n|-\n| 1991\n| ''[[Anything But Love]]''\n|\n| Episode: \"The Torrid Zone\"\n|-\n|1992\n| ''[[Grapevine (TV series)|Grapevine]]''\n| Billy\n| Episode: \"The Lisa and Billy Story\"\n|-\n|1992\n| ''[[Northern Exposure]]''\n| Glenn\n| Episode: \"Northwest Passages\"\n|-\n|1992\n| ''[[Murphy Brown]]''\n| Bo\n| Episode: \"A Year to Remember\"\n|-\n|1993\n| ''[[Mad About You]]''\n| Sam\n| Episode: \"Love Among the Tiles\"\n|-\n|1993\n| ''[[Nurses (TV series)|Nurses]]''\n| Chuck\n| Episode: \"What Are Friends For?\"\n|-\n|1993\n| ''[[Designing Women]]''\n| Craig\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n|1993\n| ''[[Love & War (TV series)|Love & War]]''\n| Duane\n| Episode: \"It Don't Mean a Thing If It Ain't Got That Swing\"\n|-\n| 1994\n| ''[[Rise and Walk: The Dennis Byrd Story]]''\n| [[Scott Mersereau]]\n| Television film\n|-\n|1995\n| ''[[Grace Under Fire]]''\n| Meter Man\n| Episode: \"A Night at the Opera\"\n|-\n|1995\n| ''[[Ellen (TV series)|Ellen]]''\n| Jack\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 1995\u201397\n| ''[[Dave's World]]''\n| Eric\n| 34 episodes\n|-\n| 1995\u201398\n| ''[[Seinfeld]]''\n| David Puddy\n| 10 episodes\n|-\n|1998\n| ''[[House Rules (1998 TV series)|House Rules]]''\n| Dan\n| Episode: \"Sex and Violence\"\n|-\n|1998\n| ''[[Maggie Winters]]''\n| Sonny\n| Episode: \"Likable Maggie\"\n|-\n| 1998\u201399\n| ''[[NewsRadio]]''\n| Johnny Johnson\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[The Apartment Co