t\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2001\n|Online Film and Television Association Award\n|Best Voice-Over Performance\n|rowspan=2|''[[The Emperor's New Groove]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Annie Award]]\n|[[Annie Award for Voice Acting in a Feature Production|Voice Acting in a Feature Production]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|2005\n|New York VisionFest Outstanding Achievement Award\n|Acting \u2013 Male\n|rowspan=3|''[[The Civilization of Maxwell Bright]]''\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2006\n|[[Boulder International Film Festival|Boulder International Film Festival Award]]\n|Best Actor\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[Beverly Hills Film Festival|Beverly Hills Film Festival Award]]\n|Best Male Performance\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|2007\n|rowspan=2|Annie Award\n|Voice Acting in an Animated Television Production\n|''[[The Emperor's New School]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|2008\n|Annie Award for Voice Acting in a Feature Production\n|''[[Bee Movie]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n{{wikiquote}}\n* {{IMDb name|nm0911320}}\n* [http://www.filmmonthly.com/Profiles/Articles/PatrickWarburton/PatrickWarburton.html Fletch Takes On \"The Puddy\"], 2004 interview by Clint Fletcher on filmmonthly.com; accessed October 31, 2014.\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Warburton, Patrick}}\n[[Category:1964 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors from New Jersey]]\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[Category:American male television actors]]\n[[Category:American male video game actors]]\n[[Category:American male voice actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Huntington Beach, California]]\n[[Category:Actors from Paterson, New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Servite High School alumni]]\n", "name_user": "2a01:e35:2ff8:b4a0:dcf3:f779:7ea2:79e2", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eVideo games)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Warburton"}
{"title_page": "Nicol\u00e1s Chiesa", "text_new": "{{short description|Argentine footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Nicol\u00e1s Chiesa\n| image       = \n| image_size  = \n| fullname    = Nicol\u00e1s Hernan Chiesa\n| birth_date  = {{Birth date and age|1980|05|26|df=y}}<ref name=SW>{{Soccerway|415852}}</ref>\n| birth_place = [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]]<ref name=SW/>\n| death_date  = \n| death_place = \n| height      = 1.66m<ref name=SW/>\n| position    = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]<ref name=SW/>\n| youthyears1 =  |youthclubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Nueva Chicago|Nueva Chicago]] \n| years1 = 2001\u20132002 |clubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Nueva Chicago|Nueva Chicago]]   |caps1 = 0  |goals1 = 0\n| years2 = 2002      |clubs2 = [[Club Almirante Brown|Almirante Brown]] |caps2 = 17  |goals2 = 1\n| years3 = 2003\u20132004 |clubs3 = [[Instituto Atl\u00e9tico Central C\u00f3rdoba|Instituto de C\u00f3rdoba]] |caps3 =  2 |goals3 = 0\n| years4 = 2004      |clubs4 = [[Ca\u00f1uelas F\u00fatbol Club|Ca\u00f1uelas]]    |caps4 =  14 |goals4 = 2\n| years5 = 2005      |clubs5 = [[FC Politehnica Ia\u0219i (1945)|Politehnica Ia\u0219i]]    |caps5 = 2  |goals5 = 0 \n| years6 = 2006\u20132008 |clubs6 = [[A.D.C. Ars et Labor Grottaglie|Grottaglie]]    |caps6 = 72  |goals6 = 31\n| years7 = 2008\u20132009 |clubs7 = [[S.S.D. Citt\u00e0 di Brindisi|Brindisi]]    |caps7 =  34 |goals7 = 6\n| years8 = 2009\u20132010 |clubs8 = [[A.C. Pisa 1909|Pisa]]    |caps8 =  27 |goals8 = 6\n| years9 = 2010\u20132011 |clubs9 = [[A.S.D. Forza e Coraggio|Forza e Coraggio]]    |caps9 = 34  |goals9 = 13\n| years10 = 2011\u20132012 |clubs10 = [[A.S.D. Martina Calcio 1947|Martina Franca]]    |caps10 =  30 |goals10 = 7\n| years11 = 2012\u20132015 |clubs11 = [[Lupa Roma F.C.|Lupa Roma]]   |caps11 = 75  |goals11 = 14\n| years12 = 2015\u20132017 |clubs12 = [[Floriana F.C.|Floriana]]    |caps12 =  63 |goals12 = 11\n|totalcaps = 370  |totalgoals = 91\n| manageryears1 = 2017\u20132018 |managerclubs1 = [[Floriana F.C.|Floriana]]\n}}\n\n'''Nicol\u00e1s Hernan Chiesa''' (born 26 May 1980) is a Argentine former footballer who played as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] and a [[Manager (association football)|manager]].<ref>{{WorldFootball|nicolas-chiesa}}</ref><ref>{{Tuttocalciatori|Chiesa_Nicolas_Hernan}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bdfa.com.ar/jugadores-NICOLAS-HERNAN-CHIESA-1028.html|title=Nicol\u00e1s Hernan Chiesa|publisher=Bdfa.com|accessdate=8 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.telekomsport.ro/povestea-fabuloasa-a-unui-fost-stranier-din-liga-1-e-prieten-la-catarama-cu-esteban-cambiasso-si-antreneaza-la-boca-juniors-19066101| title=Povestea fabuloas\u0103 a unui fost stranier din Liga 1. E prieten la cataram\u0103 cu Esteban Cambiasso \u015fi antreneaz\u0103 la Boca Juniors| publisher=Telekomsport.ro| language=Romanian|trans-title=The fabulous story of a former foreigner from Liga 1. He is a friend of Esteban Cambiasso and trains at Boca Juniors| date=20 July 2019 | accessdate=8 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.maltafootball.com/2017/12/05/nicolas-chiesa-appointed-new-floriana-fc-coach/ | title=Nicolas Chiesa appointed new Floriana FC coach| publisher=Maltafootball.com| language=Romanian | date=12 May 2017 | accessdate=8 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n===Player===\n'''Almirante Brown'''\n*[[Primera B Metropolitana|Primera B]]: 2006\u201307<ref>{{RomanianSoccer|4129/nicols-hernn-chiesa.htm}}</ref>\n'''Floriana'''\n*[[Maltese FA Trophy]]: [[2016-17 Maltese FA Trophy|2016\u201317]]<ref name=SW/>\n===Manager===\n'''Floriana'''\n*[[Maltese Super Cup]]: [[2017 Maltese Super Cup|2017]]<ref name=SW/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Chiesa, Nicol\u00e1s}}\n[[Category:1980 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Nueva Chicago footballers]]\n[[Category:Al