stan were not expected to make it out of the group after poor performances in previous championships. They were uninspiring in 2005 and the following year had little chance in a group that included powerhouses Iran and ASEAN kingpins Thailand. But with more games under their belt, the relatively young squad will be aiming for better results this year.\n\nIn March 2019, the [[Football Federation of Turkmenistan]] named [[Robert Grdovi\u0107]] as the head coach of the Turkmenistan national futsal team, signing a one year contract<ref>[https://turkmenportal.com/blog/18042/horvatskii-specialist-rober-grdovich-vozglavit-nacionalnuyu-sbornuyu-turkmenistana-po-futzalu \u0425\u043e\u0440\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0441\u043f\u0435\u0446\u0438\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0441\u0442 \u0420\u043e\u0431\u0435\u0440\u0442 \u0413\u0440\u0434\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447 \u0432\u043e\u0437\u0433\u043b\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0442 \u043d\u0430\u0446\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0443\u044e \u0441\u0431\u043e\u0440\u043d\u0443\u044e \u0422\u0443\u0440\u043a\u043c\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0430 \u043f\u043e \u0444\u0443\u0442\u0437\u0430\u043b\u0443]</ref>.\n\n==Tournament records==\n\n===FIFA Futsal World Cup===\n* [[1989 FIFA Futsal World Championship|1989]] \u2013 ''Part of Soviet Union''\n* [[1992 FIFA Futsal World Championship|1992]] \u2013 ''Did not enter''\n* [[1996 FIFA Futsal World Championship|1996]] \u2013 ''Did not enter''\n* [[2000 FIFA Futsal World Championship|2000]] \u2013 ''Did not enter''\n* [[2004 FIFA Futsal World Championship|2004]] \u2013 ''Did not enter''\n* [[2008 FIFA Futsal World Cup|2008]] \u2013 ''Did not qualify''\n* [[2012 FIFA Futsal World Cup|2012]] \u2013 ''Did not qualify''\n* [[2016 FIFA Futsal World Cup|2016]] \u2013 ''Did not qualify''\n* [[2020 FIFA Futsal World Cup|2020]] \u2013 ''TBD''\n\n===[[AFC Futsal Championship]]===\n{{see also|AFC Futsal Championship}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;font-si